<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <title>Video Game Calendar</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <style type="text/css">
      :root {
        --color-1: #f9faf4;
        --color-2: #4a6163;
        --color-3: #f9a66c;
        --color-4: #ffc94b;
        --color-5: #f17a7e;
        --max-width: 700px;
      }

      a {
        color: var(--color-5);
      }

      abbr {
        font-style: italic;
      }

      body {
        background-color: var(--color-1);
        color: var(--color-2);
        font-family: 'Nunito', sans-serif;
        font-size: 16px;
      }

      main {
        margin: 2em auto 0 auto;
        max-width: var(--max-width);
        padding: 0 1em;
      }

      .intro {
        margin: 0 0 1em 0;
      }
      .intro__title {
        font-size: 2em;
        margin: 0 0 .1em 0;
      }

      .calendar-month {
      }
      .calendar-month + .calendar-month {
        margin-top: 1.5em;
      }
      .calendar-month__title {
        background-color: var(--color-1);
        font-size: 1.5em;
        margin-top: 0;
        padding-top: 1em;
        position: sticky;
        top:  0;
      }
      .calendar-month__list {
        list-style: none;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }
      .calendar-month__list-item {
        margin: .5em 0;
      }
      .calendar-month__list-item + .calendar-month__list-item {
        border-top: 1px dashed var(--color-5);
        padding: .5em 0 0 0;
      }

      .calendar-entry {
        display: flex;
      }
      .calendar-entry__date {
        background-color: var(--color-3);
        border-radius: 6px;
        border: 1px solid var(--color-5);
        box-shadow: inset 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
        color: white;
        display: inline-block;
        flex: 0 0 auto;
        font-size: 1.1em;
        font-weight: bold;
        height: 35px;
        line-height: 35px;
        text-align: center;
        text-shadow: 0 0 3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
        width: 35px;
      }
      .calendar-entry__date--has-past {
        background-color: var(--color-5);
      }
      .calendar-entry__content {
        margin-left: 1em;
      }
      .calendar-entry__content p {
        font-size: 1em;
        font-weight: bold;
        margin: 0;
      }
      .calendar-entry__platform-list {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        font-size: .9em;
        list-style: none;
        margin: 0.3em 0 0 0;
        padding: 0;
      }
      .calendar-entry__platform-list-item {
        border-right: 1px solid var(--color-2);
        margin-right: 0.5em;
        padding-right: 0.5em;
      }
      .calendar-entry__platform-list-item:last-child {
        border-right: none;
        font-weight: 600;
        margin-right: 0;
        padding-right: 0;
      }
    </style>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Nunito:wght@400;600;700&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
  </head>
  <body>
    <main>
      <header class="intro">
        <h1 class="intro__title">Video Game Release Calendar</h1>
        <p>I wanted a way to quickly see what games are coming out without having to faff around, visiting multiple sites to check if they're correct. I also wanted it dead simple, easy to read and easy to find games. This is that attempt.</p>
        <p>It pulls content from multiple sources and tries to group games together that are the same (not everyone writes release dates and games the same).</p>
        <p>Jump to <a href="#{{ currentMonth }}">today's month</a> or <a href="#now">the closest date to today</a>.</p>
        <p>Last updated on <time datetime="{{ renderDate }}"><strong>{{ renderDate }}</strong></time>. Aggregating content from {{ &utils.renderSourcesListFormat }}.</p>
      </header>
      
      {{# calendar.months }}
        <section class="calendar-month">
          <h2 class="calendar-month__title" id="{{ name }}">{{ name }}</h2>
          <ol class="calendar-month__list">
            {{# entries }}
              <li class="calendar-month__list-item" {{# utils.entryIsNow }}id="now"{{/ utils.entryIsNow }}>
                <div class="calendar-entry">
                  <time class="calendar-entry__date {{# utils.entryDateHasPast }}calendar-entry__date--has-past{{/ utils.entryDateHasPast }}" datetime="{{ utils.entryDateToISOString }}">
                    {{ utils.entryGetDate }}
                  </time>
                  <div class="calendar-entry__content">
                    <p>{{ name }}</p>
                    <ul class="calendar-entry__platform-list">
                      {{# platforms }}
                        <li class="calendar-entry__platform-list-item">
                          <abbr title="{{ name }}">{{ shortName }}</abbr>
                        </li>
                      {{/ platforms }}
                    </ul>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </li>
            {{/ entries }}
          </ol>
        </section>
      {{/ calendar.months }}
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
